{"tid":1643170,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大獲！無人戴口罩！","createTime":"2019-10-10T04:13:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T04:20:13.000Z","uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"708aaef7eb378a42269ce0832e9f9ba28082e3ba","tid":1643170,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T04:13:59.000Z","msg":"P牌每日珍貴一post，求上熱門<br />\n<br />\n今朝返工見到得兩個人同我有戴口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔怪得有巴打發晦氣話不如完左社運佢。香港人咁簡單連戴口罩都做唔到，又唔敢衝又唔罷工又唔文宣又唔跳閘，宜家連口罩都唔戴，真係令人好想放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>但係！！！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n為左受傷同死去既手足，我地唔可以放棄，一定要宣揚到全民日日戴口罩為止！！我要所有文宣痴晒係各區連儂牆、fb、ig！每一個地方都要見到口罩文宣！！DLLM<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n戴口罩係一種無聲抗議惡法，仲可以俾大家知道有好多同路人！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>為左保障自己同他人，戴口罩啦好無呀？</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n文宣傳送門：<a href=\"https://t.me/hkstandstrong_promo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkstandstrong_promo&d=N3SWmacea4shigR4hA2Em8g1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=0c8c8cc1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkstandstrong_promo</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3wMkAdC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3wMkAdC.jpg&h=4f527131&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2AzqMkk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2AzqMkk.jpg&h=b63fb7cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ewa9tzf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fewa9tzf.jpg&h=f63cbf2b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3e99464c57abacc70e9778593953c60c1709d036","tid":1643170,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T04:14:33.000Z","msg":"點樣先肯戴口罩，係醫院都無乜人戴口罩係咩玩法"},